### Prize Claims — Confirm prize delivery after a winner is declared

### List prize claims for a week summary
### Requires weekSummaryId — copy from summaries/weeks response into http-client.env.json
GET {{host}}/api/prize-claims?weekSummaryId={{weekSummaryId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### List prize claims for a month summary
GET {{host}}/api/prize-claims?monthSummaryId={{monthSummaryId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Create a prize claim (confirm a prize was awarded)
POST {{host}}/api/prize-claims
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "weekSummaryId": "{{weekSummaryId}}",
  "rank": 1
}

###

### Mark prize claim as used/delivered
PUT {{host}}/api/prize-claims/{{prizeClaimId}}/used
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isUsed": true
}
